  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "卓群布農族人的男孩，在成長過程中，必須要經過幾個重要祭儀，一個是嬰兒祭，再者是射耳祭，另一個是成年禮。成年禮一定要經過嚴格的訓練，之後，才能成為戰士。",
      "ab": "Maca taldaingas bananaz uva’az is Bunun Takitudu ki’ a, na asat minhamu tuza’ is maipia ta’ a mantaan kasauqbungun a sinluluc’an, maca ta’a ha sumsum’uva’az ciin malaqtainga, maca ta’a ha na masumsum is taiminduu luc’anun pinaqtung. Maca luc’an pinaqtung is mintaiminduu ka bununi’ a, asa tu tutuza’un pisqanciap pintamasaz, na tudiipin maqtu’ minmalalasti’ is bunun.",
