    {
      "chinese": "在年底時，族人舉行成年禮時，長者是以夢卜來決定。儀式可分成個階段：第一階段是行動之前的祈福儀式。祈求祖靈的助佑，並觀察大地各種靈物及天象各種變化的啟示。",
      "ab": "Maca kakachun is pandiipas tatqamisan, na masumsum tuza’ is pinaqtung bununi’, makubahi’ ca madadaingaz pindaduus kukuzaun. \r\n[===]\r\nMaca sinsumsum dii ha maqtu’ pintau’un ta’ saduu. Maca ha’an taimita’a, tangausunang tuququmic masusumsum. Luluklac is maitangusin a madadaingaz maqaipu, mananailang is miniqumic ha’an kaidalaqan ti’ ciin diqanin saduu ti maiza naupa ca sinpasnava.",
      "order": "2",
